    BiocManager, Biostrings, data.table, DT, ggplot2, grid, jsonlite, reticulate,
    shiny, shinyBS, shinyFiles, shinyjs, shinyalert, shinythemes, stringr, 
    PhyloProfile (>= 1.3.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
